  "id": "RAW_ab8b7469",
  "title": "CVPR 2026 | 中科院、港中文等提出 HiFi-Inpaint：无损还原物体细节，重塑 Inpainting 生成范式！",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzA3MzI4MjgzMw==&mid=2651022970&idx=3&sn=143a4c11223060534827a2d7d0f8dd6c",
  "date": "2026-03-22 05:31:00",
  "author": "机器之心",
  "siteName": "机器之心",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p><img src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=d5668a17&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2F5L8bhP5dIqFv2mjjAePGrNKLyaPFk1YUFUDoCPYFnwz6ia6lvEsgRxlDL56nftGVfiaVvx5J1icJRm3dicS6uIbzkwib502S74sz1cI5Pmt0lIPI%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\" style=\"font-size: 1rem;\"></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">在 AIGC 领域，基于</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">参考图像的</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">图像</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">修复（Reference-based Inpainting）</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">一直是一项备受关注的核心任务，它旨在利用参考图像引导修复过程，生成视觉一致的内容。这一技术在广告营销和电商领域有着巨大的应用潜力，例如让 AI 自动生成 “真人手持或穿戴商品” 的展示图。然而，真实世界的商业应用对高保真度有着极其苛刻的要求。现有的模型在处理这类高标准任务时常常 “翻车”，尤其是在精细细节的保留上显得力不从心：品牌 Logo 扭曲、包装文字乱码、产品纹理丢失等问题，成为了阻碍技术落地的最大痛点。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">为了攻克这一难题，来自中国科学院大学、香港中文大学等机构的研究团队联合提出了</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">&nbsp;HiFi-Inpaint&nbsp;</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">模型。该工作深入探索了参考图像修复的本质，通过创新性地引入高频特征引导机制，实现了令人惊叹的高保真细节还原。目前，该项工作已被计算机视觉顶级会议</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">&nbsp;CVPR 2026</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">&nbsp;接收。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5166666666666667\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"3404\" data-height=\"1758\" data-imgfileid=\"503538740\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=c56fe0bd&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F5L8bhP5dIqEpmw1XntkyY5Rsm1bFufgOj4jzPziaoK8aKDodTltiania67hmaZDnF4w41MLYnZicW1W7N4VGGlZxIkPWQtN0lr4PM3XqYS9BR7k%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <ul style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:17px;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;margin-bottom:0px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\">\n    <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;clear: both;min-height: 1em;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75em;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:15px;\">论文标题：</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">HiFi-Inpaint: Towards High-Fidelity Reference-Based Inpainting for Generating Detail-Preserving Human-Product Images</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:17px;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;margin-bottom:0px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\">\n    <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;clear: both;min-height: 1em;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75em;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">论文链接： <a href=\"https://arxiv.org/abs/2603.02210\" target=\"_blank\">https://arxiv.org/abs/2603.02210</a>&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:17px;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;margin-bottom:0px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\">\n    <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;clear: both;min-height: 1em;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75em;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">项目主页： <a href=\"https://correr-zhou.github.io/HiFi-Inpaint\" target=\"_blank\">https://correr-zhou.github.io/HiFi-Inpaint</a></span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">🛑 行业痛点：为什么商品细节这么难搞？</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">虽然当前的扩散模型（Diffusion Models）在图像生成上取得了革命性进展，甚至能通过图像定制或文本驱动编辑来生成内容，但在处理高度定制化的 “人 + 商品” 图像时，依然力不从心 。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">现有的&nbsp;</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">“基于参考图像的图像修复（Reference-based Inpainting）”</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">&nbsp;方法提供了一个解决思路，但在实际应用中仍面临三大阻碍 ：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">1.&nbsp;</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">细节易</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">丢失</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">： 扩散模型的去噪过程倾向于将内容 “平均化” 或产生幻觉，导致纹理、形状和品牌元素（如文字）的严重不一致。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">2.&nbsp;</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">监督信号粗糙</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">： 传统的隐空间（Latent Space）MSE 损失无法提供精确到像素级别的指导，难以约束高频细节。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">3.&nbsp;</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">缺乏高质量数据</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">： 大规模、多样化且精准对齐的 “人 + 商品” 开源训练数据极度匮乏。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">💡 核心洞察与解决方案：HiFi-Inpaint</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">为了解决上述问题，研究团队提出了&nbsp;</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">HiFi-Inpain</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">t</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">。它的核心 Insight 在于：</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">既然隐空间容易丢失高频信息，那就显式地将 “高频特征” 提取出来，直接注入到网络</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">结构和损失函数中！</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.29551337359792923\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"4636\" data-width=\"4636\" data-height=\"1370\" data-imgfileid=\"503538741\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=70bfe740&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F5L8bhP5dIqGIeiaCsCJbR5C0fhkJ7dlmEiacpuLltjwhCqTsHhjoEYxuNoBEJpkVuicrsTjDe8tvNwbjuBeS9B8xzJicyVcgH0ClZzrIjhgiccxQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 13px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-style: italic;\">HiFi-Inpaint 能够将商品参考图无缝融合到带 Mask 的人物图像中，同时保持极高保真度的细节还原。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">HiFi-Inpaint 基于 FLUX.1-Dev 架构进行了深度改造 ，其三大核心创新点如下：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.3892733564013841\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"4624\" data-width=\"4624\" data-height=\"1800\" data-imgfileid=\"503538742\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=67eeb4c1&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F5L8bhP5dIqEs92CG5SbkTVTuID0goksiaFWStp0yOiaoeDnxBJO77hd15JW8NDdRvs7zO5SP7DZp91RMDdO4ibttoNKoDA22Vd68cILJsGYQD0%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 13px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-style: italic;\">HiFi-Inpaint 的整体框架，包含了数据集构建流程、高频特征提取、SEA 模块以及 DAL 损失。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">1. 结构创新：共享增强注意力（Shared Enhancement Attention, SEA）</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">为了在重绘区域精准保留商品特征，研究团队设计了共享增强注意力模块。它利用共享的双流视觉 DiT 块来细化 Mask 区域内的视觉 Token。具体而言，模型在另一个分支中将商品图像的 Token 替换为对应的高频图 Token，通过学习一个权重因子，将高频特征注入回主干网络：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.09463276836158192\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"708\" style=\"width: 321px;height: 30px;\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"503538777\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=93861978&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2F5L8bhP5dIqErf7uLHTx5gsl0UEoOU6eY5CIFsA2icSKSCP11T5AqxyxbM9UFjm48z3Ut4VsXaaSOa7oGbibqVpicyHyQk4VG62ib8aRmice500wg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">这种设计既增强了模型捕获复杂商品特征的能力，又因为参数共享机制，保持了模型的紧凑性（每个模块仅引入了一个额外参数）。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.365093499554764\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"2246\" data-width=\"2246\" data-height=\"820\" data-imgfileid=\"503538743\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=b027c3c7&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F5L8bhP5dIqETTGhwCDY62LRLES6Rk4srEDFmxswQckh6FlHicTYaYe8KtdDprOLoFakSGY5iaO51qt1AB5WdLTnOcMvl8M3LpamN1iaSNBwpJk%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 13px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-style: italic;\">采用固定的高频权重（Fixed）往往会导致特征冲突，在重绘区域产生明显的视觉伪影；而 SEA 模块巧妙地引入了可学习的权重因子（Learnable），使高频细节的注入更加平滑、自适应，最终生成的 “人 + 商品” 图像在光影与结构上更加和谐真实。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">2. 训练策略：细节感知损失（Detail-Aware Loss, DAL）</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">仅仅在模型结构上发力还不够。为了弥补隐空间监督的不足，研究团队引入了细节感知损失函数。这是一种利用高频像素级监督的损失函数：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.11128775834658187\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"629\" style=\"width: 272px;height: 30px;\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"503538778\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=b5827960&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2F5L8bhP5dIqGPhHvK5nvPE9Dwuibxh3cia2ahXxibJnmvbmgbfDJBUO6j7crtHhUwZJXTf6Ce7tZEUNUPm1dKHFkjRv5iaVUoiaEXZpoQIblZfM3c%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">它专门针对 Mask 区域内的高频成分（如文字边缘、图案纹理）进行约束，有效指导了那些难以仅通过潜在级别监督恢复的细粒度细节的重建。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.3294538943598926\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"2234\" data-width=\"2234\" data-height=\"736\" data-imgfileid=\"503538744\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=ed5df043&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F5L8bhP5dIqEBMHB4hG4vsuJ3noRrqugGAS4xI0uZiakQBFw6D4HzWlpN4ZA995nXqtC8ure6v8YzMT0c8lYQoOVohia0lWbxrOJ1sIbIHGJTE%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 13px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-style: italic;\">传统的 Canny 边缘检测会无差别地提取所有轮廓，引入大量无用的背景杂乱信息（如红框所</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 13px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-style: italic;\">示）；而 HiFi-Inpaint 采用的特定频域滤波方法（Ours）能够精准高亮商品上的关键文字、Logo 与精细</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 13px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-style: italic;\">纹理（如蓝框所示），从而为 DAL 损失提供最纯净、最精确的像素级监督信号 。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">3. 数据破局：构建 HP-Image-40K 数据集</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">为了打破数据瓶颈，团队提出了一套自动化的 “自合成与过滤” 流水线，构建了包含 4 万多张 高质量样本的数据集&nbsp;</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">HP-Image-40K</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">&nbsp;。 流程包括：使用 FLUX.1-Dev 生成双联图（左侧商品，右侧人 + 商品）-&gt; 边缘检测分割 -&gt;YOLOv8 与 CLIP 进行语义一致性过滤 -&gt; InternVL 进行文本重合度（Textual Filtering）过滤。这保证了训练数据中商品文字和形态的高度一致性。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.26458036984352773\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"2812\" data-width=\"2812\" data-height=\"744\" data-imgfileid=\"503538745\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=ea4c2bea&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2F5L8bhP5dIqFp95QRUF6En2cZaJYWs8p70oibSt2X6hmNmaWBNKTZJJBdzwzEFj8hLkyNosG6RsA47yygzsu4lbrctomvmTNE7rMictrnibiaAns%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 13px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-style: italic;\">左侧直方图展示了极为广泛的 Mask 面积占比分布，这意味着模型在训练后能自适应从 “小挂件” 到 “大物件” 的各种生成比例；右侧词云图则凸显了极其丰富的商品类别，为模型学习真实世界中千变万化的产品材质、形状和物理结构打下了极其坚实的数据基石。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">🏆 惊艳的效果对比</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">有了高频特征引导和高质量数据的加持，HiFi-Inpaint 在定量和定性评估上都展现出了统治力。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.9054852320675105\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"2370\" data-width=\"2370\" data-height=\"2146\" data-imgfileid=\"503538749\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=2537163b&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F5L8bhP5dIqG1ia2mWGGG9F7Ml4giclk17nF6bY4yqsxbe00BbD0owg0EtKKw6IqYicWgfMyuRHET32Gk8VhGLo3dPjvjQpJzwQWg4OVUpJJkYo%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 13px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-style: italic;\">与 ACE++、Insert Anything 和 FLUX-Kontext 相比，HiFi-Inpaint 能够完美还原瓶身上的微小文字、Logo 和瓶盖纹理，拒绝 “AI 幻觉”。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">在自动评估指标中，HiFi-Inpaint 在文本对齐（CLIP-T）、视觉一致性（CLIP-I 达到 0.950，DINO 达到 0.919）和结构相似度（SSIM-HF 达到 0.429）上均取得了 SOTA（State-of-the-Art） 的表现 。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.1931867184131091\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"4638\" data-width=\"4638\" data-height=\"896\" data-imgfileid=\"503538746\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=90e7f480&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2F5L8bhP5dIqEkdLcWEtvVXN21ibhOynNjYbrXTicIl6ticAibnuoP2UjibLytvTFq7CrUMrsNqehdKRcKxnGKmbIRVGnpiaU7acUsQ40mBmmROk4EA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.19412607449856734\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"2792\" data-width=\"2792\" data-height=\"542\" data-imgfileid=\"503538747\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=c8e412f9&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F5L8bhP5dIqHhFC5kZU3VXaXciaqNiaCZqrEz73A5BeYeGz76U6uo0nx5SXYg2rz579XarMpnBFyXVhjjmVsp10f4gRRFN8rN3gsRfyaTJW2q0%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 13px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-style: italic;\">HiFi-Inpaint 在多项自动评估指标上取得最佳性能（上：合成测试数据，下：真实测试数据）。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">此外，即使在更为复杂、未见过的</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">真实世界数据集</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">（包含复杂光照、遮挡、室内外场景）上，HiFi-Inpaint 依然表现出了强大的泛化能力和鲁棒性，能够自然地将目标商品融入场景并保留关键视觉属性 。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.26328125\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1280\" data-width=\"1280\" data-height=\"337\" data-imgfileid=\"503538748\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=daf3abd0&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2F5L8bhP5dIqHC5A8cnWXIu6KHAW0sYXsQvDzo3dwvhOQX012oV5kbMwiaevvgEzETSCHia1Ef2hR64CibbiaiaOt29fVho62UicUyybXhulafiaMvo8%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 13px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-style: italic;\">图注：无论是户外无人物理环境、大姿态全身视角、复杂商品遮挡，还是大幅度的风格迁移（如漫画风），HiFi-Inpaint 都能游刃有余。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">🌟 总结与思考 (Takeaways)</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">HiFi-Inpaint 的出现，为电商海报生成、商品虚拟试用等商业落地场景扫清了一大障碍。它的成功给我们带来了两个核心启发：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">1.&nbsp;</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">高频信号不可忽视</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">： 在生成模型全面走向高保真度要求的今天，单纯依赖网络 “自己领悟” 隐空间特征在某些任务中是不够的。显式地引入传统图像处理中的先验（如通过傅里叶变换提取高频图），能为模型提供极其精准的 “锚点”。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">2.</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">&nbsp;Data-Centric AI 依然奏效</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">： 利用大模型进行自动化数据合成与多重严格过滤，并进行自蒸馏学习，是突破领域数据匮乏的高效途径。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">目前该工作已被顶级计算机视觉会议 CVPR 2026 接收。期待未来能在更多商业和视频生成场景中看到它的身影。</span></span></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "中科院与港中文团队提出 HiFi-Inpaint 模型，通过显式高频特征引导机制解决电商场景「人+商品」图像生成中的细节丢失难题，已被 CVPR 2026 接收。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "中科院与港中文团队提出 HiFi-Inpaint 模型，通过显式高频特征引导机制解决电商场景「人+商品」图像生成中的细节丢失难题，已被 CVPR 2026 接收。",
  "summary": "本文介绍了一个针对电商场景的高保真图像修复模型 HiFi-Inpaint。现有扩散模型在生成「人+商品」图像时常出现品牌 Logo 扭曲、文字乱码、纹理丢失等问题。研究团队创新性地引入高频特征提取机制，将其直接注入网络结构和损失函数。该模型基于 FLUX.1-Dev 架构，提出了共享增强注意力（SEA）模块和细节感知损失（DAL），并构建了包含 4 万样本的 HP-Image-40K 数据集。在多项自动评估指标上达到 SOTA 表现，能在复杂场景下保持商品细节的高保真还原。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "显式高频特征引导机制是解决细节丢失的关键",
      "explanation": "传统隐空间 MSE 损失无法精确约束高频细节，HiFi-Inpaint 通过傅里叶变换提取高频图，直接注入网络结构和损失函数，为模型提供精准的像素级锚点。"
    },
    {
      "point": "SEA 模块实现了高频特征的自适应注入",
      "explanation": "共享增强注意力模块通过可学习权重因子，将商品图像的高频特征平滑注入重绘区域，避免了固定权重导致的特征冲突和视觉伪影。"
    },
    {
      "point": "DAL 损失提供了高频像素级监督",
      "explanation": "细节感知损失采用特定频域滤波方法，精准提取商品上的文字、Logo 和纹理边缘，避免了传统 Canny 边缘检测引入的背景噪声。"
    },
    {
      "point": "自动化数据合成流水线突破了数据瓶颈",
      "explanation": "通过 FLUX.1-Dev 生成双联图、边缘检测分割、YOLOv8 与 CLIP 语义过滤、InternVL 文本重合度过滤，构建了高质量的 HP-Image-40K 数据集。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
    "既然隐空间容易丢失高频信息，那就显式地将「高频特征」提取出来，直接注入到网络结构和损失函数中！",
    "采用固定的高频权重往往会导致特征冲突，在重绘区域产生明显的视觉伪影；而 SEA 模块巧妙地引入了可学习的权重因子，使高频细节的注入更加平滑、自适应。",
    "传统 Canny 边缘检测会无差别地提取所有轮廓，引入大量无用的背景杂乱信息；而 HiFi-Inpaint 采用的特定频域滤波方法能够精准高亮商品上的关键文字、Logo 与精细纹理。",
    "在生成模型全面走向高保真度要求的今天，单纯依赖网络「自己领悟」隐空间特征在某些任务中是不够的。",
